Text: Don't bother.  This is a scam to get you to go to a porn site to get the full clip.  It has a huge strip at bottom of screen for an ad that never goes away.  This is the new scam to make a few bucks for down loaders.

These idiots really annoy me.  Do they seriously believe that the downloaders are going to go to a porn site and pay money to see the rest of a posted clip??!!!

Just have to keep an eye out for the next username this idiot assumes to try and scam the honest TPB users.
